    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>泳ぎの練習、しておいてくださいね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Please practice swimming.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……わかった。
努力はしてみる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I understand. I'll do my best.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ねぇ、リアラ。
せっかくだからセネルさんも
“白”として仲間に入ってもらおうよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, Reala. Since he's already here,
we could have Senel join us as "White".</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そ、そうだな。
クーリッジも仲間に入れて貰えると
私としては嬉しいと言うか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-I agree. I'd be happy if Coolidge could
be counted among our allies here, too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>俺はべつに……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't really...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だめ。
セネルはいらないの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We can't.
Senel can't join.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんでだ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why not?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>太古より伝わるこの本によると
“白”は途中加入らしいの。
だから初期メンバーにはいらないわ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Based on this ancient book that's been
handed down, "White" seems to have
joined the team later on. That means he
can't join as an initial member.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>その本……ホントに
太古から伝わるものなの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Has that book...
really been passed down since ancient times?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
